author: Nathan Layne
title: New York reports 779 more deaths, governor says social distancing working
description: New York's efforts at social distancing are working to get the coronavirus outbreak under control even as the state reported an additional 779 deaths, a record high for a second day, the Governor Andrew Cuomo said on Wednesday.
content:
